{"tid":1246303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下一隊開記者會既球隊係邊個高官/部門？","createTime":"2019-06-20T15:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T15:51:41.000Z","uid":56889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9d50322d50bf5c50fa5d48c4086f736d0fcc49c7","tid":1246303,"uid":56889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"近日第五屆香港特別行政區政府球賽，鬥得十分激烈。<br />\n繼盧Sir、林太同阿超後，梁生又再加入混戰。<br />\n<br />\n盧Sir帶領既畜龍隊威到街知巷聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W8EY25K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW8EY25K.jpg&h=9d66c1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有同盧Sir叮噹馬頭既林太有信心三年內奪冠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDJZNxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDJZNxv.jpg&h=9292b55b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然阿超唔想參加, 無奈場波因佢而起冇法啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6yrsxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6yrsxB.jpg&h=eb15b3c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鍾意買魚蛋落前線探醫護人員既梁生亦都唔汁輸, 決定玩埋一份<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJfA5jk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJfA5jk.jpg&h=11e51f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一隊係邊個呢？而最後贏家到底係邊個呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S22jNxK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS22jNxK.jpg&h=9c67ecb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>部份改圖源自其他巴打</strong>"}]}